        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "In addition to the benefits of journeybread, power journeybread grants you a +1 item bonus to Athletics checks to Climb, Force Open, and Swim, and to Fortitude saving throws against being sickened. The number of minutes you can Hustle changes to your Constitution modifier \u00d7 20. These benefits last for 4 hours.",
